abstracts.cdata!:
This transcript, from the session of the
            Executive Directors of the International Bank for
            Reconstruction and Development (IBRD) and International
            Development Association (IDA) held on Tuesday, June 26, 1973
            covers only the discussion on the Third Education Project
            Credit for Ethiopia.
